name: The Agenda Mix
description:
The Agenda Mix

Yes, that's it the "TRANS AGENDA" - because not only do we have Dissociative Identity disorder, we're also Nonbinary/Transmasculine.

So this model is to CELEBRATE CIVIT AI's diversity, Generation sites please be aware this is a merge, and we want to give space to those who helped make these mixes.

SUPPORT US:

If SOMEHOW CIVIT ISN'T WORKING WE WILL ALWAYS HAVE A BACKUP: https://huggingface.co/Duskfallcrew/AgendaMix
